Hello @datapythonista! Thanks for updating the PR.

 - There are no PEP8 issues in the file [`pandas/core/frame.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/core/frame.py) !

 - In the file [`pandas/core/panel.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/core/panel.py), following                are the PEP8 issues :
> [Line 1042:13](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/core/panel.py#L1042): [E731](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E731) do not assign a lambda expression, use a def

 - In the file [`pandas/core/window.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/core/window.py), following                are the PEP8 issues :
> [Line 1380:13](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/core/window.py#L1380): [E731](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E731) do not assign a lambda expression, use a def


 - There are no PEP8 issues in the file [`pandas/io/gbq.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/io/gbq.py) !

 - In the file [`pandas/io/json/json.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/io/json/json.py), following                are the PEP8 issues :
> [Line 893:13](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/pandas/io/json/json.py#L893): [E731](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E731) do not assign a lambda expression, use a def


 - There are no PEP8 issues in the file [`scripts/generate_pip_deps_from_conda.py`](https://github.com/datapythonista/pandas/blob/75b89eba2067914bf8d1acc97f7318fa6a080c32/scripts/generate_pip_deps_from_conda.py) !
